jodi total weight of a graph negative hoi then oita negative weight cycle hisebe
count hobe and dijkstra negative value handle korte pare jdi negative weight
cycle na thake..

jodi negative weight cycle thake then amra ekta different algorithm use kori
bellmen ford algorithm.


So , BFS er sob undirected ,directed graph er shortest path ver kore jekhane DFS just traverse kore
BFS weighted graph e weight nite pare na tai Dijkstra algorithm use kore hoi..
then update asche Dijkstra algorithm negative weight nie kaj korte parleo negative weight cycle hole infinite bar cholte thke (negative weight uporoe define kora hoeche)
tai eita update hochhe Bellman ford algorithm.

BFS --- > weighted graph
Dijkstra > negative weight cycle
Bellman ford > sob node ke source dhore shortest distance ver krte gele time complexity onk vere jay tai next updaate e etao fix kora jay 
